quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"Yubassarunehum yeveddulmucrimu lev yeftediy min ﾂｴazabi yevmeizin bibeniyhi"
  70,12,"Ve sahﾄｱbetihi ve ehﾄｱyhi"
  70,13,"Ve fasﾄｱyletihilletiy tuﾂｴviyhi"
  70,14,"Ve men fiylﾂｴardﾄｱ cemiyﾂｴan summe yunciyhi"
  70,15,"Kella inneha leza"
  70,16,"Nezzaﾂｴaten liﾅ淒歹va"
  70,17,"Tedﾂｴu men edbere ve tevella"
  70,18,"Ve cemaﾂｴa feevﾂｴa"
  70,19,"ﾄｰnnelﾂｴinsane hulika heluﾂｴan"
  70,20,"ﾄｰza messehuﾅ淒歹rru cezuﾂｴan"
  70,21,"Ve iza messehulhayru menuﾂｴan"
  70,22,"ﾄｰllelmusalliyne"
  70,23,"Elleziynehum ﾂｴala salatihim daimune"
  70,24,"Velleziyne fiy emvalihim hakkun maﾂｴlumun"
  70,25,"Lissaili velmahrumi"
  70,26,"Velleziyne yusaddikune biyevmiddiyni"
  70,27,"Velleziyne hum min ﾂｴazabi rabbihim muﾅ殲ikune"
  70,28,"ﾄｰnne ﾂｴazabe rabbihim ﾄ歛yru meﾂｴmunin"
  70,29,"Velleziyne hum lifurucihim hafizune"
  70,30,"ﾄｰlla ﾂｴala ezvacihim ev ma meleket eymanuhum feinnehum ﾄ歛yru melumiyne"
  70,31,"Femenibteﾄ歛 verae zalike feulaike humulﾂｴadune"
  70,32,"Velleziyne hum liemanatihim ve ﾂｴahdihim raﾂｴune"
  70,33,"Velleziyne hum biﾅ歹hadatihim kaimune"
  70,34,"Velleziyne hum ﾂｴala salatihim yuhafizune"
  70,35,"Ulaike fiy cennatin mukremune"
  70,36,"Femalilleziyne keferu kﾄｱbeleke muhtﾄｱﾂｴﾄｱyne"
  70,37,"Anilyemiyni ve ﾂｴaniﾅ淒殃mali ﾂｴﾄｱziyne"
  70,38,"Eyatmeﾂｴu kullumriin minhum en yudhale cennete naﾂｴﾄｱymin"
  70,39,"Kella inna halaknahum mimma yaﾂｴlemune"
